{"tid":1733632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[車公]尋日為poly手足求籤","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:39:11.000Z","uid":236079,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2aec62a0d184502d06cde54f0068db126537cf1","tid":1733632,"uid":236079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"車公靈簽 第十五簽：中籤<br />\n<br />\n簽文：斧斤持以入山林，未得之時那處尋；損了良材失卻力，勸君留住待春臨。<br />\n<br />\n解簽：家宅平吉，占病作福，婚姻不合，自身平安，求財未遂<br />\n<br />\n斷簽：家宅不安，占病拖延，自身運滯，出入無功，婚姻不合，求財虧本，時衰命蹇，徒勞無功，萬事守舊，靜待時至<br />\n<br />\n好準。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫大家等候，唔好亂行動。<br />\n只供參考！"},{"pid":"4ffe787a2a23ba05caad99c88da5ce51576c5429","tid":1733632,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92409f5581925aed792220a896b5736b06aed364","tid":1733632,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"事後諸葛亮 唔琴日post？"},{"pid":"2f0eddf58b910d1edcb7971841ab71ff8ded648b","tid":1733632,"uid":236079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92409f5581925aed792220a896b5736b06aed364","tid":1733632,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"事後諸葛亮 唔琴日post？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"尋日post有用？你地會因此唔去救？<br />\n咁你覺得而家有無參考價值？"},{"pid":"31f9e0c7ad0da04f6b0f3fd490025852e533f759","tid":1733632,"uid":327204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f0eddf58b910d1edcb7971841ab71ff8ded648b","tid":1733632,"uid":236079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92409f5581925aed792220a896b5736b06aed364","tid":1733632,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"事後諸葛亮 唔琴日post？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"尋日post有用？你地會因此唔去救？<br />\n咁你覺得而家有無參考價值？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"而家post 有用？ 你收下皮